    • Enum Constant Detail

      • INT_DELTA_RECURSIVE

        public static final FloatCodecs INT_DELTA_RECURSIVE
        Encoding a list of floats (e.g. coordinates) using integer encoding (3DP accuracy), delta encoding and then recursive indexing.

      • INT_RUNLENGTH

        public static final FloatCodecs INT_RUNLENGTH
        Encoding a list of floats (e.g. occupancy) using integer encoding (2DP accuracy) and then run length encoding.
